data.description: ***MOTIVATED SELLER*** Price reduction. Immaculate, barely used townhouse is ready for you! This cozy townhouse located in Davenport has a beautiful kitchen with stainless steel appliances, refrigerator, microwave, dishwasher, stove, dryer and washer all included. Electric water heater, granite countertop, the open concept that gives you the beautiful opportunity to connect closely with family and friends right from your kitchen. The 3 bedrooms, spacious master suite with a large walk-in closet, 2.5 bathrooms,  1 car Garage. Extremely well and distributed layout space, that is close to Disney, restaurants and marketplace. The Madison Place community offers a dog park community pool, playground, HOA that maintains your front and back yard. Which comes in handy for a peaceful living space. The builder has SOLD OUT, don't miss this great opportunity, perfect for 1st. time home buyer or Investment Property!   Only minutes  from Highway I-4, US 27.
